# Docker Compose security overlay for claude-code-hermit.
#
# Generated by /claude-code-hermit:docker-security from operator selections
# stored in .claude-code-hermit/config.json under docker.security.*.
#
# Apply via the hermit-docker wrapper, which auto-detects this file and
# chains it with the base compose:
#   .claude-code-hermit/bin/hermit-docker up
#
# Or manually:
#   docker compose -f docker-compose.hermit.yml \
#                  -f docker-compose.security.yml up -d
#
# Reverse with /docker-security (answer No to every prompt) or by deleting
# this file. The wrapper script no-ops on absence; baseline hardening from
# v1.0.26 (cap_drop, no-new-privileges, pids_limit) is in the base compose
# and is unaffected by this overlay.
#
# Conditional sections below are rendered or omitted based on the operator's
# choices. Sections marked {{...}} with placeholders are rendered with real
# values at overlay-render time.

